name: Morphometrics Support Code
tagline: Various R scripts and functions for morphometrics data collection and analysis (complement for geomorph)
body: On this page you can find R scripts that perform various functions for morphometrics data collection and analysis. They are usually to be used as a complement to [geomorph R package](http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/geomorph/).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
